      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-09T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 1980,
      "representative_excerpt": "I am a concerned citizen of Louisiana, a state where the regulation of marine commerce has important effects on our economy. I have concerns about this proposed rule. The U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service says the definition has led to inconsistent treatment and an unnecessary regulatory burden. Where? To who? Only vague references to \u201cinconsistent treatment\u201d a...",
