      "page_count": 1,
      "representative_comment_id": "FWS-HQ-LE-2026-0628-0009",
      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-11T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 468,
      "representative_excerpt": "Removing the phrase \"having a shell\" is ideal and should be done since it does create confusion to people who then think that lobster and crab are the similar to oyster and clam. <br/><br/>I am in favor of that aspect but I DO NOT think you should include cephalopods under the term shellfish since that will create additional confusion. These species are harv...",
